{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>警方到場調查，證實該名女子過馬路期間不慎跌倒，傷及腰部，意外不涉及交通意外；她由救護車送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1124033709939494912107295.jpeg/VkOicIQRfwl5B7Ay0ctwDVaYp72pfQQuVHdJIlR3SSI\" alt=\"女子受傷躺在馬路上。（網上相片）\"><figcaption>女子受傷躺在馬路上。（網上相片）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260423/1124033707124985856168203.jpeg/EB-8vkhSG2XWSX7RlaAQVHguZ3fNZcFxV8Cf4VfAn-E\" alt=\"有路經人士上前協助。（網上相片）\"><figcaption>有路經人士上前協助。（網上相片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T10:12:39.822431+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":88,"images":2,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}